title: Nate Rebolledo from Xibalba & Bryan Garris from Knocked Loose (live from Outbreak Fest)
itunes:title: Nate Rebolledo from Xibalba & Bryan Garris from Knocked Loose (live from Outbreak Fest)
description:
LIVE FROM OUTBREAK FEST 2022, IT'S 100 WORDS OR LESS! 

Jokes aside, I am so pleased to bring you this chat with two heavy hitters in the hardcore scene for my first live podcast experience at the incredible Outbreak Festival in Manchester, UK. I sat down with Nate from Xibalba and Bryan from Knocked Loose to hang out and talk about touring Europe, hardcore in 2022 and so much more. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
